
"smart_sources:Research/@qian_isolation_1990.md": {"path":"Research/@qian_isolation_1990.md","last_embed":{"hash":null},"embeddings":{},"last_read":{"hash":"1xqjwia","at":1774951884833},"class_name":"SmartSource","last_import":{"mtime":1774951829735,"size":1934,"at":1774951884833,"hash":"1xqjwia"},"blocks":{"#---frontmatter---":[1,56],"#Isolation and identification of two new pyrone compounds from the culture of Herictum erinaceus":[58,62],"#Isolation and identification of two new pyrone compounds from the culture of Herictum erinaceus#{1}":[60,62]},"outlinks":[{"title":"Author/Fu-Gang Qian","target":"Author/Fu-Gang Qian","line":45},{"title":"Author/F. G. Qian","target":"Author/F. G. Qian","line":46},{"title":"Author/Guoyong Xu","target":"Author/Guoyong Xu","line":47},{"title":"Author/G. Y. Xu","target":"Author/G. Y. Xu","line":48},{"title":"Author/Shou-ying Du","target":"Author/Shou-ying Du","line":49},{"title":"Author/S. J. Du","target":"Author/S. J. Du","line":50},{"title":"Author/M. H. Li","target":"Author/M. H. Li","line":51},{"title":"Author/M. H. Li","target":"Author/M. H. Li","line":52}],"metadata":{"id":"qian_isolation_1990","type":"article-journal","title":"Isolation and identification of two new pyrone compounds from the culture of Herictum erinaceus","issued":{"date-parts":[[1990]]},"DOI":"null","container-title":"Acta pharmaceutica Sinica","abstract":"Four crystalline and one liquid compounds were isolated from the solid cultured extract of Hericium erinaceus, Two of them are new, named herierin Ⅲ and Ⅳ. Their chemical structures were determined as 6-methy 1-2,5-dihydroxymethyl-γ-pyranone (Ⅲ) and 2-hydroxymethy 1-5-a-hydroxy-ethyl-γ-pyranone (Ⅳ). The others are 4-chloro-3, 5-dimethoxybenzoic-O-arabitol ester, 4-chloro-3, 5-dimethoxybenz0ic methyl ester and 4-chloro-3,5-dimethoxybenzoic acid. In addition, a mixture of palmic and stearic acid, a mixtrue of behenic acid and tetracosanic acid and a mixture of 5α-ergostan-3-one, 5α-stigmasten-22-en-3-one and 5α-stigmastan-3-one were also isolated.","tags":["#literature_note"],"author":[{"family":"Qian","given":"Fu-Gang","literal":""},{"family":"Qian","given":"F. G.","literal":""},{"family":"Xu","given":"Guoyong","literal":""},{"family":"Xu","given":"G. Y.","literal":""},{"family":"Du","given":"Shou-ying","literal":""},{"family":"Du","given":"S. J.","literal":""},{"family":"Li","given":"M. H.","literal":""},{"family":"Li","given":"M. H.","literal":""}],"citation-key":"qian_isolation_1990","year":"1990","dateCreated":"2026-03-31","reading-status":"to-read","aliases":["Isolation and identification of two new pyrone compounds from the culture of Herictum erinaceus"],"author-links":["[[Author/Fu-Gang Qian]]","[[Author/F. G. Qian]]","[[Author/Guoyong Xu]]","[[Author/G. Y. Xu]]","[[Author/Shou-ying Du]]","[[Author/S. J. Du]]","[[Author/M. H. Li]]","[[Author/M. H. Li]]"],"attachment":[],"related":[[]]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},
